name: Kavyansh Gupta
about:
I am Kavyansh, A student researcher and Entrepreneur and 1 out of 32 Individuals to have been granted an opportunity to work with NASA’s Space Apps Research Cohort for an entire year starting October 2024. 
The overarching research interest is about Artificial intelligence being able to serve as a catalyst of economic and technical growth in tangential ways. When it is accompanied by powerful machines like drones, I believe It can encompass technical capabilities of billion dollar satellites. My current projects are centered around the basic concepts of intelligent systems that lay foundation for my future plans. In my recent projects, I intend to utilize ability of artificial intelligence and data science to predict the trends in stock market and recommend business new sales channels to invent on. 
My current project, " Caelum Unlimited" deals with the development of a AI-flown drone swarm which runs on lunar and solar energy depending on different time on the day by converting them into electricity and fulfilling its payload requirement. Using Holographic Projectors, these drones will be enable to create visualizations at a height which can be used for various purposes including advertising.
I am also engaged in the development of a highly accurate LSTM stock prediction model. Subsequently, I intend to establish a trust-based hedge fund. This fund will collect resources from willing investors and pool them for investment in stocks. The investment decisions will be based on the output generated by the LSTM model. The profits generated from these investments will be distributed among the investors.
I am open to collaborating on projects within my expertise that address economic and technological challenges. If you share an interest in AI, drone technology, or innovative solutions to complex problems, feel free to connect with me!
